where. We don't have a land use map of saying, no,

06:50.242 --> 06:53.126
you can only go here. Changes have occurred in the 
master plan, in the maps, and in zoning to

06:53.927 --> 06:58.753
accommodate those industries. As a result of 
their relocation. As a result of their proposal to

07:00.736 --> 07:05.402
come to the city, having been recruited by the 
Chamber of Commerce. How about the role of heavy

